{
  "stem": "2522.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nothing was happening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody entrenched would say well, you know, where is Strassman?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he's disappeared, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Come back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so my family came back on the-- I think on the 25th or the 26th of August.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] By that time of course we blew that escape plan number one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the night of the 27th of August, a Russian squad stopped a German train that was going from Berlin to Bucharest in a small railroad station where you put water into the tenders in order to go over the mountains, the Carpathian Mountains.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small squad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I happened to know everybody on that squad because I met them su-- subsequently.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was largely a Russian squad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They stopped a train while it was being refilled with water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to their surprise, they found that the sleeping cars were full of German general officers who were on their way from a staff meeting in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they took them out, shot them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The next morning, the Gestapo tried to, to implement their plan, namely disarm the Slovak army because they felt that this was a signal for the uprising.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, the Slovak army didn't want to be disarmed and overwhelmed the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the military just fled to the mountains, and the guerrillas just went, said, ah, this is the uprising.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they started executing the uprising plan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When this is happening, the Gestapo locally starts taking hostages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everyone gets taken.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father gets taken as a hostage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- that night, purely by happenstance, sleeping at the house of a friend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, this was not planned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly why, but it was just-- you know, things were crowed.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
